            <h2 class="section-title">Publications</h2>
            <div class="pub-list">
                <div class="pub-item">
                    <h3 class="pub-title">HeartSimSage: Attention-enhanced graph neural networks for accelerating cardiac mechanics modeling</h3>
                    <p class="pub-authors">Shi L*, Chen Y, Vedula V</p>
                    <p class="pub-journal"><em>Journal of Computational Physics</em>, 2026</p>
                    <p class="pub-desc">Introduces the HeartSimSage framework for AI-accelerated cardiac biomechanical simulations.</p>
